minuman vitamin sajakah?

64
00:05:08,030 --> 00:05:10,675
Saya cakap persahabatan kami
dah pun tamat.

65
00:05:12,250 --> 00:05:13,975
Macam mana saya nak tarik balik?

66
00:05:15,910 --> 00:05:18,815
