Dia jawab.

705
00:51:38,010 --> 00:51:39,279
Dia jawab!

706
00:51:39,280 --> 00:51:40,915
Awak tak tahu pun saya di mana.

707
00:51:45,180 --> 00:51:47,379
- Hei.
- Mari kita berlawan.

708
00:51:47,380 --> 00:51:49,855
Kalau saya tak lepaskan
kemarahan melalui sukan...

709
00:51:51,430 --> 00:51:52,839
