741
00:53:23,260 --> 00:53:25,719
- Awak rasa saya sedang bergurau?
- Bertenanglah.

742
00:53:25,720 --> 00:53:27,079
Sudahlah.

743
00:53:27,080 --> 00:53:29,939
Mari kita dua lawan sekarang!

744
00:53:29,940 --> 00:53:31,179
Saya pergi dulu.

745
00:53:31,180 --> 00:53:33,159
- Kita lawan dulu.
- Kenapa kita perlu berlawan?

746
00:53:33,160 --> 00:53:35,895
- Awak nak ke mana?
- Lepaskan saya.

747
00:53:42,440 --> 00:53:43,635
Minum!

748
00:53:47,760 --> 00:53:49,705
Berkongsi minuman dengan saya
pun awak tak nak?

749
00:53:50,310 --> 00:53:52,475
Kenapa awak lembab sangat?

750
00:53:53,390 --> 00:53:57,005
Satu lagi projek berkumpulan
dan awak akan jadi kaki botol.

751
00:53:57,840 --> 00:53:59,075
Seronoknya.

752
00:54:00,480 --> 00:54:02,995
Saya harap Soo-hyun ada di sini.

753
00:54:05,490 --> 00:54:08,405
Tapi kalau dia ada, kita tak boleh cakap
tentang zaman kanak-kanak So-bin.

754
00:54:11,480 --> 00:54:15,405
Sekarang giliran Yeo Jun.

755
00:54:19,180 --> 00:54:20,375
Saya

756
00:54:21,860 --> 00:54:23,365
